finding the levitt group location of the levitt group information on how to get to stanford can be found at the visitor information pages including driving directions the levitt group is in room s210 s211 and s212 of the clark center directions to clark center and zoomed map which is part of the medical center shown on the viscinity map parking around the department requires a permit the building is entered from the inner doors 2nd floor to find the levitt group go through two sets of doors then turn right and go to the end of the hallway s210 is directly on your left
